reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for walkway and bright. looks amazing as well!!
reviews.reviewText: I am very pleased with these lights. I have been looking for something to put it in my walkway and these are perfect! Perfect size from view and bright enough to get job done. The fact that you can simply plug them in with the included usb cord is a bonus! I have shown these to my friends and family and they said they would be buying some in the near future. These are nice little LED lightbars with 3 brightness levels, motion detector, and a sticky strip to attach it with magnectic connector. I love how they automatically come on when I walk by. So far I haven't had to recharge them, so the charge goes a long time!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wish I found these sooner!
reviews.reviewText: I was visiting my sister in Ohio and noticed she had under counter lighting in kitchen which was on a sensor. When I asked her about it she shared this product with me. I ordered my set as soon as I returned home. These lights are wonderful!!! I used 5 of them under my kitchen cabinets and one is under my hutch. Charging is a breeze with the stand that will charge 3 of the 6 units at the same time. They show red when you put them in the charger and once they are fully charged it changes to blue. Installation was so simple and only took a few minutes. I wish I had found this product sooner. It has changed my kitchen for the better.

reviews.reviewText: I would have given this product five stars, but one of the lights no longer works after one month of use. It doesn't charge but when on the charger it lights up blue like it’s charged. The second it’s removed from the charger the light turns red.Also I had to purchase a little bit stronger double-sided adhesive tape because the lights kept falling with what was provided in package.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These lights are amazing. When my husband first opened the box, he said he wanted me to return them. When he played around with them and saw all the light they gave off, he said never mind returning this, I know what to do with them. I took a nap and when I woke, I went looking for hubby and noticed that he had been busy putting lights under the kitchen cabinets, in the bathrooms, and in closets. I love that if I wake up in the middle of the night, I don't have to put the big light on. Instead, as I start walking toward the bathroom the two lights give me the exact light I need without totally waking me up.

reviews.reviewText: When I first purchased, I thought there were only 3 lights included but there are actually 6 !! Boy was I excited as I was planning on ordering another pack if I liked them ! They are bright and will work perfectly for lighting up my crystal displays ! I decided I didn't want to use the adhesive with that came on them and am switching for velcro so I can easily remove for charging. Love that im not fussing with batteries anymore since that gets so expensive when you keep them on all the time. They charge really quickly too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A step above your typical motion sensor light
reviews.reviewText: These lights are lightweight, built well, have a strong magnet built in and are smarter than your typical motion sensor lights. I have gone through a lot of cheap motion sensor lights and they have either broke from falling or have to be charged very frequently that its not worth using them any more. I splurged on these and they haven't let me down. They hold their charge a very long time, I have yet to charge on and it has been over a week. The coolest feature about these lights is that you can set them to turn on only in the daytime, only in the nighttime or any time it senses motion. I set it to only turn on at night so it doesn't waste battery during the day when its light out. Another cool feature is that these lights will turn back on immediately if needed. My other lights just stayed off and I stood there in the dark waving my hands around trying to get it to come back on again. These have quickly become my favorite sensor lights.
